+/*
+ * Implementation of safe memory reclamation scheme using
+ * quiescent states.
+ *
+ * This is dervied from the "GUS" safe memory reclamation technique
+ * in FreeBSD written by Jeffrey Roberson. The original copyright
+ * is preserved below.
